&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/slh-logo-150-x-150px-for-online-white-background.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-5191&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/slh-logo-150-x-150px-for-online-white-background.png&quot; alt=&quot;slh-logo-150-x-150px for online white background&quot; width=&quot;79&quot; height=&quot;79&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/a&gt;Small Luxury Hotels of the World&trade; is an unrivaled portfolio of some of the world&rsquo;s finest small independent hotels. Comprising over 520 hotels in more than 70 countries, the diversity of the individual hotels, and the experiences that they offer, is exceptional. From cutting-edge design hotels to palatial 17th century mansions, city center sanctuaries to remote private islands, historic country houses to idyllic resorts, Small Luxury Hotels of the World offers only the very best.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Surrounded by gleaming white houses under a deep blue sky and with the caldera literally across the street, Aressana Spa Hotel and Suites is a truly inviting place. Smart contemporary interiors with rich colours provide warmth throughout, while a stunning outdoor pool surrounded by daybeds and a pool bar are essential for soaking up the island sun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As a Diners Club cardmember, enjoy an automatic upgrade to &amp;#8220;Loved&amp;#8221; membership status and valuable benefits in The Club, SLH&amp;#8217;s loyalty program.&nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Before making a reservation, it is important to &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/partners/dcinternational/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;visit Small Luxury Hotels of the World&amp;#8217;s website&lt;/a&gt; and&nbsp;follow the link to join&nbsp;The Club.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Enjoy a one-year complimentary membership as a Loved Member, with benefits including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Priority &amp;#038; complimentary room upgrade on every stay (subject to availability at check-in)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complimentary daily continental breakfast for two&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late check-out on every stay (subject to availability at check-in)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to exclusive Club rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to Club Concierge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Take advantage of the &amp;#8220;Loved&amp;#8221; membership status offer by using rate code&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;SLHDCI15&lt;/strong&gt; (only necessary when reserving by phone)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reservations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;After you &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/partners/dcinternational/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;register for the Loved status&lt;/a&gt;, you will receive a Loved membership number via email. &nbsp;You will receive a membership card after your first stay at a Small Luxury Hotels property.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Visit the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/hotels/aressana-spa-hotel-and-suites/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;hotel&amp;#8217;s website&nbsp;on SLH.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;and login to your Loved membership account to make a reservation for this hotel or call SLH (visit the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/contact-us/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Contact Us page&lt;/a&gt; to find your local number) and provide rate code &lt;strong&gt;SLHDCI15&lt;/strong&gt; (only necessary when reserving by phone)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: #293033;&quot;&gt;Terms &amp;#038; Conditions&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Rates are subject to availability, which may vary by hotel, by season and by day of the week.&nbsp;Cardmembers will be advised if a partner rate is available at the chosen hotel for chosen dates when searching &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/partners/dcinternational/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;online&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or when speaking with a reservation agent.&nbsp;Complimentary room upgrade and late check-out are subject to availability at time of check-in.&nbsp;Cancellation policies, payment policies and all other booking conditions will be advised at the time of booking.&nbsp;Prepayment/deposit with your Diners Club card is required at time of booking. This amount is non-refundable in the event of cancellation or change of dates of stay. The offer is non-transferable, non-combinable and valid for new bookings only.&nbsp;Please refer to&nbsp;&lt;a title=&quot;SLH's Terms &amp;#038; Conditions&quot; href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/club/terms-and-conditions/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;SLH&amp;#8217;s Terms &amp;#038; Conditions&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;for more information.&lt;/p&gt;
